{"tid":2311787,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"CHANEL涉虛假廣告在上海被罰20萬元　普通面膜乳霜宣傳能美白祛斑","createTime":"2020-12-04T10:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T14:46:29.000Z","uid":22452,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b519e872791fe2101e51d1977ccf3de550e0d2","tid":2311787,"uid":22452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"01 唔貼link<br />\n<br />\nChanel 繼賺錢炒人、用tvb藝人之後又多單<br />\n<br />\n送都唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n著名法國時裝品牌CHANEL中國分公司，近日被上海靜安區市場監督管理局行政處罰20萬元，理由是發布虛假廣告。<br />\n內地傳媒報道指，CHANEL被罰是因廣告中使用與美白、祛斑的字眼，但實際上相關產品只是普通化妝品，做法屬於誤導消費者購買，並且已引起兩宗消費者投訴案件。<br />\n據了解，涉事化妝品共有兩款，其中一款為在2016年12月起銷售的「香奈兒奢華精粹乳霜（輕盈）」，CHANEL在官方網站上宣稱「護膚功效：&hellip;&hellip;色斑淡化」。另一款是2018年3月起銷售的「香奈兒光采晚安修護面膜」，有「護膚功效：&hellip;&hellip;2.抑制黑色素」、「產品配方：&hellip;&hellip;抑制色素-白梅精粹抑制黑色素生成是光采晚安修護面膜的第二大核心功效&hellip;&hellip;」等描述。"},{"pid":"c955cd756dcca6fe9173176541554fbed11fbfc3","tid":2311787,"uid":361975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"罰得廿萬，賣個袋賺返有突啦"},{"pid":"bd929bd291c59b8149b8fffbe2a172fe1b9240ca","tid":2311787,"uid":375569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"唔知又要炒幾多人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a299f62e3c81eeba29e278906b411d6b7f98cce1","tid":2311787,"uid":22452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"仆街公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42f4c4ac501da45d45207cc868d094ae451d665","tid":2311787,"uid":263148,"like":0,"d